|GKO================================================================
                            |RKBLunge
|GKO================================================================

|YKOLunge is the basic attack power of the wolf form. When lunging,
the wolf has the potential to do more damage than normal for
a short time. However, this comes at the price of a penalty
to dodge incoming blows.

|RKOSyntax: |YKBlunge [<target>]     |WKOCost: |CKO10 sp
